title: Very Breyeresque
description: Dan and Will return after their vacations to catch up on what they've missed. After checking in briefly on Justice Breyer, they try to talk about two of the Court's biggest cases from the end of the Term. They only manage to get through one of them: Brnovich v. DNC.
author: pod@dividedargument.com (Will Baude & Dan Epps)
